Package: Mona
Title: Single Cell RNA Visualization/Exploration
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given="Konrad",family="Thorner",email="Konrad.Thorner@cchmc.org",role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny app for analyzing single cell RNA-seq data, built upon the outputs generated by 'Seurat'. The key feature is the easy and flexible plotting interface, where users can create multiple interactive plots of multiple types at once. Other functions include the ability to subset cells, annotate clusters, calculate markers, find associated GO terms, and more. 
License: `use_mit_license()`
